description: Unofficial Hanselminutes, a weekly podcast with Scott Hanselman. Listen to the latest episode, navigate back and forth through the archive. Ask for episodes by specifying a month. Play a specific episode number. Get the latest technology update without moving a finger.This skill is neither sponsored neither endorsed by Scott Hanselman.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Hanselminutes fan for the latest episode.
Alexa, ask Hanselminutes fan to play episode number 333.
Alexa, ask Hanselminutes fan to list episodes from March.
name: Hanselminutes Fan Podcast
shortDescription: Skill made by Hanselminutes fan to bring you your favorite show on Alexa enabled devices.
